{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "rewardly-api-collection",
    "name": "Rewardly API",
    "description": "Complete Postman collection for the Rewardly gamified rewards backend.\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Import this collection into Postman.\n2. Run **Admin Login** or **Google Sign-In** — tokens auto-save to collection variables.\n3. Use protected requests; `{{token}}` / `{{adminToken}}` are applied automatically.\n\n**Variables:**\n- `baseUrl` — default `http://localhost:5000/api`\n- `token` — user JWT (auto-set after Google Sign-In)\n- `adminToken` — admin JWT (auto-set after Admin Login)\n- `userId` — MongoDB user ID for admin routes\n- `notificationId` — notification ID for mark-as-read",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:5000/api",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "adminToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "userId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "notificationId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Google Sign-In",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (json.token) {",
                  "        pm.environment.set('token', json.token);",
                  "        console.log('User token saved to environment: token');",
                  "    }",
                  "    if (json.user && json.user.id) {",
                  "        pm.environment.set('userId', json.user.id);",
                  "        console.log('User ID saved to environment: userId');",
                  "    }",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response contains token', function () {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('token');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"idToken\": \"{{googleIdToken}}\",\n  \"referredBy\": \"{{referredBy}}\",\n  \"deviceToken\": \"{{deviceToken}}\",\n  \"deviceName\": \"Pixel 8\",\n  \"deviceModal\": \"Google Pixel\",\n  \"deviceUniquCode\": \"unique-device-uuid-123456\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/google",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "google"]
            },
            "description": "Verify Google ID token and issue a user JWT.\n\n**idToken** — obtained from Google Sign-In on the mobile client (Google OAuth). This is NOT generated by the backend; copy it from your app's Google Sign-In response.\n\n**referredBy** (optional) — referrer's `referCode` (e.g. `REWARDLY-abc12`). Only applied on first signup.\n\n**deviceToken** (optional) — FCM device token for push notifications.\n\nOn success, `token` and `userId` are auto-saved to collection variables."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "description": "Public authentication endpoints."
    },
    {
      "name": "User APIs",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Home",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/home",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["home"]
            },
            "description": "Returns home screen data for the logged-in user including points, referral info, alert banner, and prize amounts from Settings."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Leaderboard (Today)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/score?type=today",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["score"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "type",
                  "value": "today",
                  "description": "today | monthly"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Leaderboard sorted by `todayGamePoints` descending. Returns top 50 plus the logged-in user's rank."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Leaderboard (Monthly)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/score?type=monthly",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["score"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "type",
                  "value": "monthly",
                  "description": "today | monthly"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Leaderboard sorted by `monthGamePoints` descending."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Reward History",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/rewards/history?page=1&limit=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["rewards", "history"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "20"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Paginated reward history for the logged-in user, newest first."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Winners (Today)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/winners?type=today",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["winners"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "type",
                  "value": "today",
                  "description": "today | monthly"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Winner records for today, joined with user name and profilePic, sorted by rank."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Winners (Monthly)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/winners?type=monthly",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["winners"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "type",
                  "value": "monthly",
                  "description": "today | monthly"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Winner records for the current month."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Notifications",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (json.data && json.data.length > 0 && json.data[0]._id) {",
                  "        pm.environment.set('notificationId', json.data[0]._id);",
                  "        console.log('notificationId saved:', json.data[0]._id);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/notifications?page=1&limit=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["notifications"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "20"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Notifications relevant to the user (broadcast + targeted), paginated, newest first, with `isRead` flag.\n\nAuto-saves first notification `_id` to `{{notificationId}}` for mark-as-read testing."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Mark Notification Read",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/notifications/{{notificationId}}/read",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["notifications", "{{notificationId}}", "read"]
            },
            "description": "Marks a notification as read for the logged-in user.\n\nUses `{{notificationId}}` — run **Get Notifications** first to auto-populate it."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Play Game",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"pointsEarned\": 50\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/game/play",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["game", "play"]
            },
            "description": "Deducts 1 from `leftGame`, adds points to `todayGamePoints` and `monthGamePoints`, logs GameHistory and RewardHistory.\n\nReturns 400 if `leftGame` is already 0."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Device Token",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"deviceToken\": \"{{deviceToken}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/user/device-token",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["user", "device-token"]
            },
            "description": "Updates the logged-in user's FCM device token. Call on every app login/open."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Dismiss User Alert",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"userId\": \"{{userId}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/user/alert/false",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["user", "alert", "false"]
            },
            "description": "Dismiss/hide the homepage alert banner for this user by setting alert to false. If `userId` is omitted in the body, it defaults to the authenticated user from the token."
          },
          "response": []
        }
        ,
        {
          "name": "Redeem Code (v1)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"REWARDLY-XXXX\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/user/redeem",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["user", "redeem"]
            },
            "description": "Redeem a voucher or referral code. Uses same controller as `/user/redeemcode` — kept for compatibility."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Redeem Code (legacy)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"REWARDLY-XXXX\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/user/redeemcode",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["user", "redeemcode"]
            },
            "description": "Legacy redeem endpoint kept for older clients — maps to the same backend handler as `/user/redeem`."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ],
      "description": "User-facing endpoints. All require `Authorization: Bearer {{token}}`."
    },
    {
      "name": "Admin APIs",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Admin Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (json.token) {",
                  "        pm.environment.set('adminToken', json.token);",
                  "        console.log('Admin token saved to environment: adminToken');",
                  "    }",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Response contains token', function () {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('token');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{adminEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["admin", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Admin email + password login. Issues a separate admin JWT.\n\nOn success, `adminToken` is auto-saved to collection variables.\n\nDefault seeded credentials: `admin@rewardly.com` / `Admin@123456` (from `.env`)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Dashboard",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/dashboard",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["admin", "dashboard"]
            },
            "description": "Summary stats: total users, points distributed, today's top 3, month's top 3, winners, notifications count."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Users",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (json.data && json.data.length > 0 && json.data[0].id) {",
                  "        pm.environment.set('userId', json.data[0].id);",
                  "        console.log('userId saved:', json.data[0].id);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/users?page=1&limit=20&search=&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["admin", "users"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "20"
                },
                {
                  "key": "search",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Search by name or email"
                },
                {
                  "key": "sortBy",
                  "value": "createdAt",
                  "description": "name | email | todayGamePoints | monthGamePoints | createdAt | referCount"
                },
                {
                  "key": "sortOrder",
                  "value": "desc",
                  "description": "asc | desc"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Paginated list of all users with search and sort.\n\nAuto-saves first user's `id` to `{{userId}}`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get User By ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/users/{{userId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["admin", "users", "{{userId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Full profile of one user including GameHistory and RewardHistory.\n\nUses `{{userId}}` — run **Get Users** or **Google Sign-In** first to populate it."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Toggle Block User",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/users/{{userId}}/block",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["admin", "users", "{{userId}}", "block"]
            },
            "description": "Toggles block/unblock status for a user. No request body required."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Settings",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/settings",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["admin", "settings"]
            },
            "description": "Returns the current Settings document (alert, prizes, referAmount, dailyGameLimit)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Settings",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"alert\": true,\n  \"alertTitle\": \"Today big offers\",\n  \"alertDescription\": \"Aaj sabse bada offer hai. Aaj ke din user ko 2x points diye jayenge\",\n  \"dailyFirstPrice\": 50,\n  \"dailySecondPrice\": 30,\n  \"dailyThirdPrice\": 20,\n  \"monthlyFirstPrice\": 500,\n  \"monthlySecondPrice\": 300,\n  \"monthlyThirdPrice\": 100,\n  \"referAmount\": 50,\n  \"dailyGameLimit\": 5\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/settings",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["admin", "settings"]
            },
            "description": "Update app settings. All numeric fields must be positive. All fields are optional — only send what you want to change."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Send Notification (Broadcast)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"New Offer Alert\",\n  \"description\": \"Play today and earn double points on every game!\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/notification",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["admin", "notification"]
            },
            "description": "Broadcast notification to all users. Omit `targetUser` to send to everyone via FCM multicast."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Send Notification (Single User)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Personal Reward\",\n  \"description\": \"You have earned a special bonus! Check your rewards.\",\n  \"targetUser\": [\"{{userId}}\"]\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/notification",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["admin", "notification"]
            },
            "description": "Send notification to a specific user. `targetUser` must be a valid MongoDB ObjectId."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Finalize Winners (Daily)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"type\": \"daily\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/winners/finalize",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["admin", "winners", "finalize"]
            },
            "description": "Manually finalize daily winners (top 3 by todayGamePoints), create Winner + RewardHistory records, send push notifications, then reset todayGamePoints and leftGame for all users."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Finalize Winners (Monthly)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"type\": \"monthly\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/winners/finalize",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["admin", "winners", "finalize"]
            },
            "description": "Manually finalize monthly winners (top 3 by monthGamePoints), then reset monthGamePoints for all users."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Winners",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{adminToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/winners",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["admin", "winners"]
            },
            "description": "View today's daily winners and this month's monthly winners (admin view with full user details)."
          },
